node.text:
On some days I’m a multi-tasking procrastinator. I can put off multiple things at once. 🤪 Today is one of those off days and I'm feeling like a zombie 🧟‍♂️
.
.
#Baileyfurball #BaileyBlues #CircuitBreakerSg
Wow, just when I thought you couldn’t get any cuter!
We think you a really cool  good looking Zombie , come on friend let’s go play .🐾🐾❤️🐾🐾
cutest zombie i ever did see!
You live a hard life 🙊 so cute
Haha yep me and my mom are putting everything off today 😆
Cutest zombie 🧟‍♀️ I’ve ever seen.... these days are making me tired 😴 and I think I’m becoming a multi-tasking procrastinator too!! 😂😂
Awww happy lazy day ❤️❤️❤️ sweet dreams 😘
I feel exactly the same cutie 😂💗
Same. I haven’t gotten out of bed all day.
